1250:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c **** /**
1251:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  @brief      Get one packet from the FIFO.
1252:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  If @e sensors does not contain a particular sensor, disregard the data
1253:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  returned to that pointer.
1254:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  \n @e sensors can contain a combination of the following flags:
1255:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  \n INV_X_GYRO, INV_Y_GYRO, INV_Z_GYRO
1256:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  \n INV_XYZ_GYRO
1257:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  \n INV_XYZ_ACCEL
