1261:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  return a non-zero error code.
1262:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  @param[out] gyro        Gyro data in hardware units.
1263:MyHardWare/eMPL/inv_mpu_dmp_motion_driver.c ****  *  @param[out] accel       Accel data in hardware units.
